Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Networked multiplayer poker game supporting draw, stud,
 and community-card variants, including Texas Hold'em and Omaha,
 with optional wild cards. The deal rotates around the table, and
 the dealer chooses the game before each hand.
